ContentType.Name: Page
ContentType.Description: Page is a system content type template created by the Publishing Resources feature. The column templates from Page will be added to all Pages libraries created by the Publishing feature.

ContentType.Name: Article Page
ContentType.Description: Article Page is a system content type template created by the Publishing Resources feature. It is the associated content type template for the default page layouts used to create article pages in sites that have the Publishing feature enabled.

ContentType.Name: Welcome Page
ContentType.Description: Welcome Page is a system content type template created by the Publishing Resources feature. It is the associated content type template for the default page layout used to create welcome pages in sites that have the Publishing feature enabled.

ContentType.Name: Error Page
ContentType.Description: Error Page is a system content type template created by the Publishing Resources feature. It is the associated content type template for the default page layouts used to create error pages in sites that have the Publishing feature enabled.

ContentType.Name: Approved Shared News Page
ContentType.Description: This content type is intended for use via the MSIT supported Enterprise News Service solution. Use only for solutions that cannot use the "Approved Shared News Item" content type and requires a page. Content using this type will be available in the News Service Web Part.

ContentType.Name: COE Page
ContentType.Description: Used for creation of pages in the Office 365 Center of Excellence.

ContentType.Name: Approved Shared Page
ContentType.Description: Use this content type to create a new managed page. The column templates from Managed Page will be added to all Managed Pages libraries created by the Publishing feature.

ContentType.Name: Catalog-Item Reuse
ContentType.Description: The Catalog Item Reuse content type is best if you want to create article pages that can be easily reused or republished across your site collections.

ContentType.Name: Approved Shared Article Page
ContentType.Description: Use this content type to create a new managed article page. It is the associated content type template for the default managed page layouts used to create managed article pages in sites that have the Publishing feature enabled.

Field.Name: PublishingStartDate
Field.Description: Scheduling Start Date is a site column created by the Publishing feature. It is used to specify the date and time on which this page will first appear to site visitors.

Field.Name: PublishingExpirationDate
Field.Description: Scheduling End Date is a site column created by the Publishing feature. It is used to specify the date and time on which this page will no longer appear to site visitors.

Field.Name: PublishingContact
Field.Description: Contact is a site column created by the Publishing feature. It is used on the Page Content Type as the person or group who is the contact person for the page.

Field.Name: PublishingContactEmail
Field.Description: Contact E-mail Address is a site column created by the Publishing feature. It is used on the Page Content Type as the e-mail address of the person or group who is the contact person for the page.

Field.Name: PublishingContactName
Field.Description: Contact Name is a site column created by the Publishing feature. It is used on the Page Content Type as the name of the person or group who is the contact person for the page.

Field.Name: PublishingContactPicture
Field.Description: Contact Picture is a site column created by the Publishing feature. It is used on the Page Content Type as the picture of the user or group who is the contact person for the page.

Field.Name: PublishingRollupImage
Field.Description: Rollup Image is a site column created by the Publishing feature. It is used on the Page Content Type as the image for the page shown in content roll-ups such as the Content By Search web part.

Field.Name: Audience
Field.Description: Target Audiences is a site column created by the Publishing feature. It is used to specify audiences to which this page will be targeted.

Field.Name: PublishingIsFurlPage
Field.Description: If checked, the physical URL of this page will not appear in search results. Friendly URLs assigned to this page will always appear.

Field.Name: SeoBrowserTitle
Field.Description: Browser Title is a site column created by the Publishing feature. It is used as the title that appears at the top of a browser window and may appear in Internet search results.

Field.Name: SeoMetaDescription
Field.Description: Meta Description is a site column created by the Publishing feature. Internet search engines may display this description in search results pages.

Field.Name: SeoKeywords
Field.Description: Meta Keywords

Field.Name: RobotsNoIndex
Field.Description: Hide from Internet Search Engines is a site column created by the Publishing feature. It is used to indicate to search engine crawlers that a particular page should not be indexed.

Field.Name: PublishingPageImage
Field.Description: Page Image is a site column created by the Publishing feature. It is used on the Article Page Content Type as the primary image of the page.

Field.Name: PublishingPageContent
Field.Description: Page Content is a site column created by the Publishing feature. It is used on the Article Page Content Type as the content of the page.

Field.Name: SummaryLinks
Field.Description: Summary Links is a site column created by the Publishing feature. It is used on the Welcome Page Content Type to display a set of links.

Field.Name: ArticleByLine
Field.Description: Byline is a site column created by the Publishing feature. It is used on the Article Page Content Type as the byline of the page.

Field.Name: ArticleStartDate
Field.Description: Article Date is a site column created by the Publishing feature. It is used on the Article Page Content Type as the date of the page.

Field.Name: PublishingImageCaption
Field.Description: Image Caption is a site column created by the Publishing feature. It is used on the Article Page Content Type as the caption for the primary image displayed on the page.

Field.Name: SummaryLinks2
Field.Description: Summary Links 2 is a site column created by the Publishing feature. It is used on the Welcome Page Content Type to display a second set of links.

Field.Name: _Author
Field.Description: The primary author
Used for short descriptions of news items as part of the Approved Shared News Content Type.
Field.Name: NewsDescription

Field.Description: Body of the news article goes in this field.
Field.Name: NewsArticleContent

Field.Description: Used by the Enterprise News Service to identify featured news stories.
Field.Name: FeaturedNews

Field.Description: Identify the source of the news item.
Field.Name: NewsSource

Field.Description: Identify the type of news item.
Field.Name: NewsType

Field.Description: Tag the Enterprise News item with one or more topics for filtering and targeting. Please select a closest match, only add new terms if there is nothing. Note: terms may be modified and merged by the Enterprise News management team.
Field.Name: NewsTopic
MSProducts
Field.Description: Click on the "Tags" icon to the right of this field to browse and select from all available terms. A Microsoft-wide property for tagging content with Microsoft products and technologies.

A property for tagging content with Profession and Discipline values, based on HR taxonomy. Primary purpose is for content targeting. Click on the "Tags" icon to the right of this field to browse and select from all available terms.
Field.Name: EmployeeRole
MSPhysicalGeography
Field.Description: Click on the "Tags" icon to the right of this field to browse and select from all available terms. A Microsoft-wide property for tagging content for the physical region it's about or intended for. Maps to physical regions provided by RE&F.

Field.Name: _dlc_DocId
Field.Description: The value of the document ID assigned to this item.

Field.Name: _dlc_DocIdUrl
Field.Description: Permanent link to this document.

Field.Name: _dlc_DocIdPersistId
Field.Description: Keep ID on add.

Field.Name: ReportOwner
Field.Description: Owner of this document

Field.Name: Confidentiality
Field.Description: Used to specify restrictions on the extent to which content can be exposed.

Field.Name: TaxKeyword
Field.Description: Enterprise Keywords are shared with other users and applications to allow for ease of search and filtering, as well as metadata consistency and reuse

Field.Name: RatingCount
Field.Description: Number of ratings submitted

Field.Name: AverageRating
Field.Description: Average value of all the ratings that have been submitted

Field.Name: MSEmployeeInterests
Field.Description: Click on the "Tags" icon to the right of this field to browse and select from all available terms. A Microsoft-wide property that aligns with the "Skills, Interests and Resposibilies" term set also used to populate employee profiles.
Click on the "Tags" icon to the right of this field to browse and select from all available terms. A property for tagging with sales regions.
Field.Name: SalesGeography

Field.Description: Roles for which this page applies to.
Field.Name: COEAudienceRole

Field.Description: Products to which this Page's content apply to.
Field.Name: COEProducts

Field.Description: Parent topics to which this page relates to.
Field.Name: COEParentTopic
RatedBy
Field.Description: Users rated the item.

Field.Name: Ratings
Field.Description: User ratings for the item

Field.Name: CheckedOutUserId
Field.DisplayName: ID of the User who has the item Checked Out

Field.Name: LinkCheckedOutTitle
